1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,120
Ijkuak Jesús yotlan kijtoua in tlajtlamach*,

2
00:00:08,120 --> 00:00:14,640
okis inuan inomachtijkauan* niman oyajkej ipan on okse ilado on río itoka Cedrón.

3
00:00:14,640 --> 00:00:20,560
Ompa onkatka sen kojtlakijloj kampa Jesús okalak inuan inomachtijkauan*.

4
00:00:20,560 --> 00:00:21,340
Judas,

5
00:00:21,340 --> 00:00:23,920
on yejuan kitemaktiliskia Jesús,

6
00:00:23,920 --> 00:00:26,040
no tlaixmatiya ompa,

7
00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:31,600
pampa Jesús miyekpa onosentlalitoya inuan inomachtijkauan* ompa ne.

8
00:00:31,600 --> 00:00:35,640
Niman Judas oajsik ompa inuan miyekej soldados.

9
00:00:35,640 --> 00:00:46,080
Niman no okinuikak sekimej ipolicías on ueyitiopan yejuan oualajkej ikan intlanauatil on fariseos* niman intlayekankauan on tiopixkej.

10
00:00:46,080 --> 00:00:51,840
Yejuamej yayaj ikan armas niman kitkiyaj inlámparas niman okopiltin.

11
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:55,760
Pampa Jesús ye kimatstikatka tlinon ipan nochiuas,

12
00:00:55,760 --> 00:00:58,040
ouajla okinnamikiko,

13
00:00:58,040 --> 00:00:59,760
niman okintlajtoltij:

14
00:00:59,760 --> 00:01:02,460
—¿Akinon nenkitejtemouaj?

15
00:01:02,460 --> 00:01:04,120
Yejuamej okijlijkej:

16
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:06,960
—Jesús nazareno.

17
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:08,280
Jesús okinmijlij:

18
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:11,120
—Nejua niJesús nazareno.

19
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:12,120
Judas,

20
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:16,240
on yejuan okitemaktilij Jesús no ompa inuan nemiya.

21
00:01:16,240 --> 00:01:18,160
Niman ijkuak Jesús okinmijlij:

22
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:21,400
“Nejua niJesús nazareno”,

23
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:24,080
oajketsteuetstiajkej ipan tlajli.

24
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:27,040
Kemaj Jesús oksejpa okintlajtoltij:

25
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:29,160
—¿Akinon nenkitejtemouaj?

26
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:31,680
Niman yejuamej okijtojkej:

27
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:33,960
—Jesús nazareno.

28
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:35,560
Niman Jesús okinmijlij:

29
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:38,080
—Yonemechijlij ika nejua.

30
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:40,400
Tla nejua nennechtejtemouaj,

31
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:43,920
tla ijkon in oksekimej xkinkauilikan ma uiyan.

32
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:48,120
In onochiu san para onocumpliroj on tlen Jesús okijtoka:

33
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:53,440
“On yejuan otinechinmakak nion se xopoliu.”

34
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:54,920
Kemaj Simón Pedro,

35
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:57,440
yejuan kipiyaya sen espada,

36
00:01:57,440 --> 00:02:02,800
okixikopintiaj niman okitekilij iyekmanakas sen tlakatl itoka Malco.

37
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:08,400
Yejua itlakeual katka on más ueyi tlayekanki itech on tiopixkej.

38
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:11,320
Pero Jesús okijlij Pedro:

39
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:13,920
—Xkalakti moespada kampa otikixtij.

40
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:19,900
¿Tlen tiknemilia xijki noneki nitlajyouis ken noTajtsin okitlalij para nitlajyouis?

41
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:27,960
Kemaj on miyekej soldados iuan intlayekankau niman impolicías on hebreos* okajsikej Jesús,

42
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:29,800
niman okisalojkej.

43
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:32,640
Kemaj okuikakej itech Anás.

44
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:39,980
Anás imontaj katka Caifás yejuan ipan on xipan más ueyi tlayekanki katka intech on tiopixkej.

45
00:02:39,980 --> 00:02:51,160
Caifás sano yejua okinmijlijka on hebreos* ika más kuajli para yejuamej tla mikis se tlakatl ipampa on país.

